==Russian==
===Etymology===
From [[муж]] (muž), ''man''.

===Pronunciation===
{{SAMPA|mu'Zik}}

===Noun===
'''мужик''' (mužík) {{m}}, [[мужики]] (mužikí) {{p}}

# [[boor]]
# [[coarse]], [[uncouth]] person
# [[man]]
#''(historical)'' [[peasant]]

